OL,3,GCentral, Tayside & Fife
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FIt will be a cloudier day, with
OL,6,Fsome outbreaks of rain, this mostly
OL,7,Flight but perhaps a few heavier
OL,8,Foutbreaks developing over Fife. Rather
OL,9,Fhumid.
OL,10,
OL,11,CTonight:FA mainly cloudy evening with
OL,12,Fsome patchy rain. This dying out
OL,13,Ftonight with some clear spells
OL,14,Fdeveloping along with some mist or low
OL,15,Fcloud.
OL,16,
OL,17,CTuesday:FAny low cloud burning off to
OL,18,Fleave a dry bright day with some sunny
OL,19,Fspells. Very warm.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
