OL,4,
OL,5,COutlook for Wednesday to Friday:
OL,6,FWednesday will be sunny and very warm.
OL,7,FSunny, hot inland Thursday, coastal
OL,8,Fhaar, perhaps some thundery showers
OL,9,Flater. Showery on Friday.
